03,"uid":23848,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"985cbe9ccf89b38dceb7d1a0f7c3d6754089719a","tid":1663003,"uid":270563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T04:53:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:32:39.000Z","msg":"全部都係打工<br />\n年收入6萬～20萬<br />\n買最貴個位朋友入手990萬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:01:58.000Z","msg":"年收入定月入<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:18:10.000Z","msg":"佢應該打漏咗<br />\n十二分之一年"},{"pid":"531d6eb1be6bdf6f849337503cc6d461aab46091","tid":1663003,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:18:36.000Z","msg":"[實用]    香城online防具升級詳細篇<br />\n<br />\n近呢一個月，我見到多左好多新入香城online嘅玩家，勇武/和理非都有好多工作做，鑑於有好多人唔知點配搭防具，眼見好多手足都只用貴價6092X，除左冇必要之外仲晒左好多錢，故此我係度再講一次點去配合適的防具。<br />\n<br />\n防毒面具：<br />\n中後/後防(物資站/噴漆師/文宣組/美化工程組/網上資訊組)<br />\n首選最合符經濟效益<br />\n包括單咀<br />\n3200/HF-52+3311K-55<br />\n一set最平100港幣有找<br />\n雙咀：<br />\n6200+6001/6003/6005(6005唔需要特登買，成本價貴)+5n11/5p71(唔建議5p71,如果要嘅不如買502再搭P100綿抵啲)+501蓋<br />\n例如：6200+6001CN+5n11+501 我見100已經有一set<br />\n而且 就算唔用5n11同501蓋 都ok 6001CN一對最平$30，我見$50通常都有<br />\n6003貴少少 $70成平價(睇你有冇運見到)<br />\n以上都可以頂到TG，但記得聞到味要即換<br />\n<br />\n想了解更多快啲入去連登睇啦😛<br />\n...<br />\n防毒面具篇完<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666931</a>"},{"pid":"a955ac53b14abb3034ef574867eac8e5df3ec628","tid":1663003,"uid":217542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:25:14.000Z","msg":"[突發] 北角好似有手足出事<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665948\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665948</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n幫手推 冇媒體報導 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85d1a60cbc8860e94e744aeb85c079509db54f08","tid":1663003,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:35:05.000Z","msg":"中產買幾多都得啦<br />\n係小康基層買戇鳩啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b89b713ed9e840bb2652b36c31d1e90cde9c78d5","tid":1663003,"uid":327892,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:37:51.000Z","msg":"真係咁多人做 aa咩?真係咁好景，就唔使係咁上連登唱啦。<br />\n<br />\n又話連登仔無錢移民又無錢買樓，咁上嚟唱把託咩，打多幾個 cold call好過啦。3萬幾個 agent，你估真係個個都揾到咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcd768a3fb27809f280a15f3f40b5ec0e5a00b2d","tid":1663003,"uid":309879,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:48:00.000Z","msg":"自住怕咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc94660e0019418c4476783141689896e228f701","tid":1663003,"uid":324739,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e29bac092287fb6508785edaf83a18bf755959af","tid":1663003,"uid":4934,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"a3d8a3e6a1b259cfde56794d4b1c9745f137e3a8","tid":1663003,"uid":23848,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"985cbe9ccf89b38dceb7d1a0f7c3d6754089719a","tid":1663003,"uid":270563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T04:53:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:32:39.000Z","msg":"全部都係打工<br />\n年收入6萬～20萬<br />\n買最貴個位朋友入手990萬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:45:22.000Z","msg":"年收入六萬都買到樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:22:51.000Z","msg":"唔食唔洗 買層600萬既樓都供成百年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e59d6d6d7d38d2d86d332de1294ebcb674b3101b","tid":1663003,"uid":279356,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:21:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h93TUgu.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh93TUgu.gif&h=2b5b378f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"11f1eae5c1e8742b34a1